    "body": "[`void gpr_set_log_function(gpr_log_func f)`](https://github.com/grpc/grpc/blob/master/include/grpc/support/log.h#L84) may be used as an opt-out solution:\r\n```\r\nvoid BlackholeLogger(gpr_log_func_args* args) {}\r\n...\r\ngpr_set_log_function(BlackholeLogger);\r\n```"
